{
  "text": "In this paper, we propose another method for constructing the BCJ numerators based on the Cachazo-He-Yuan (CHY) formula [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and the polynomial scattering equations [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . The CHY form, which is a compact representation of scattering amplitudes, in general takes the following form at tree level for n external particles,",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "5970885",
    "[CITATION_2]": "53685436",
